c0000000
00:00:00.630 --> 00:00:03.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[dramatic piano music]</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:04.300 --> 00:00:06.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, why don't we kiss?</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:08.430 --> 00:00:10.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The girl who says things
like that to tease me.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:15.890 --> 00:00:16.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait a minute.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:17.480 --> 00:00:19.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who was she, again?</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:19.190 --> 00:00:21.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[yawns]</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:29.110 --> 00:00:31.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is written hereafter
to be honest</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:31.530 --> 00:00:34.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is something you might find
completely unbelievable.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:35.160 --> 00:00:37.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But everything
is true so make sure</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:37.370 --> 00:00:39.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to read until the very end.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:39.620 --> 00:00:40.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have to.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:42.040 --> 00:00:43.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's all this?</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:44.290 --> 00:00:48.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>May 6th, I encountered
a wild bunny girl.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:50.880 --> 00:00:52.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm?</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:52.680 --> 00:00:55.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:55.720 --> 00:00:58.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[The Peggies' "Kimi no sei"]</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:58.640 --> 00:01:05.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000017
00:01:40.980 --> 00:01:47.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:07.340 --> 00:02:14.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:41.700 --> 00:02:42.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:43.040 --> 00:02:44.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:53.880 --> 00:02:55.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What the heck is that?
- [shushes]</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:55.840 --> 00:02:57.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000023
00:03:03.890 --> 00:03:04.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000024
00:03:08.730 --> 00:03:10.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How interesting.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:03:10.110 --> 00:03:12.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So then I take it you're
still able to see me?</b></Default>

c0000026
00:03:12.610 --> 00:03:14.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000027
00:03:14.240 --> 00:03:16.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, goodbye.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:03:17.070 --> 00:03:18.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000029
00:03:19.490 --> 00:03:23.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're, uh, Sakurajima-senpai,
right?</b></Default>

c0000030
00:03:23.790 --> 00:03:25.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Since you're referring to me
as senpai,</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:25.790 --> 00:03:28.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that means you must be a student
at Minegahara High School.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:29.040 --> 00:03:32.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm Sakuta Azusagawa,
class 2-1.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:32.460 --> 00:03:34.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You spell my first name like
"blooming taro"</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:35.050 --> 00:03:36.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and my last name like
the rest stop.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:37.260 --> 00:03:39.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't remember asking that.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:39.300 --> 00:03:42.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can call me Mai Sakurajima,
spelled just like it sounds.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:42.760 --> 00:03:44.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I know that.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:44.140 --> 00:03:45.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're a celebrity, after all.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:46.060 --> 00:03:48.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll give you
this one warning.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:48.350 --> 00:03:50.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Forget about what
you saw here today</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:53.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and don't involve yourself
with me under any circumstances.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:53.900 --> 00:03:55.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:55.440 --> 00:03:57.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you understand that,
then say yes.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:57.400 --> 00:03:58.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [stammers]</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:59.280 --> 00:04:00.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000046
00:04:06.290 --> 00:04:08.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000047
00:04:12.590 --> 00:04:15.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> - She told me to forget, but...</b></Default>

c0000048
00:04:17.090 --> 00:04:18.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [breathing deeply]
- Kaede, it's morning.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:04:18.760 --> 00:04:20.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wake up.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:04:20.300 --> 00:04:21.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groaning]</b></Default>

c0000051
00:04:21.720 --> 00:04:23.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please let me stay, big brother.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:04:23.470 --> 00:04:24.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm freezing.
- No, thanks.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:04:24.680 --> 00:04:25.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both groaning]</b></Default>

c0000054
00:04:25.970 --> 00:04:27.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Half of Kaede's made
of her feelings</b></Default>

c0000055
00:04:27.350 --> 00:04:28.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for you, big brother!</b></Default>

c0000056
00:04:28.810 --> 00:04:31.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Stop saying such
embarrassing things.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:31.730 --> 00:04:34.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think you're a little too old
to be climbing into my bed.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:34.480 --> 00:04:35.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not normal
for kids your age.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:35.980 --> 00:04:37.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know that?</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:37.610 --> 00:04:39.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is it 'cause it gets you
too excited in the morning?</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:39.990 --> 00:04:42.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Who would get excited over
his actual little sister?</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:42.820 --> 00:04:45.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[train car rattling]</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:47.660 --> 00:04:48.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Question.</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:50.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you like bunny girls, Kunimi?</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:50.830 --> 00:04:52.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I mean, not exactly.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:52.580 --> 00:04:54.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Okay, do you love them?</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:54.340 --> 00:04:55.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, yeah.
You bet I do.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:56.250 --> 00:04:58.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So if you were to bump into
an attractive bunny girl</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:58.550 --> 00:05:01.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the library,
what would you do?</b></Default>

c0000070
00:05:01.260 --> 00:05:03.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm, a double-take?
- Right?</b></Default>

c0000071
00:05:03.470 --> 00:05:06.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then I would gawk at her.
- Right.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:05:18.190 --> 00:05:19.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Kunimi.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:05:19.900 --> 00:05:22.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can see Sakurajima
a bit ahead of us, right?</b></Default>

c0000074
00:05:22.490 --> 00:05:24.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yep, crystal clear.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:05:24.120 --> 00:05:26.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I wonder what kind
of person she is.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:05:27.040 --> 00:05:29.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mm, she's a celebrity,
isn't she?</b></Default>

c0000077
00:05:29.450 --> 00:05:31.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, yeah, she is.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:05:31.750 --> 00:05:34.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Despite being on hiatus,
she's still in show biz, right?</b></Default>

c0000079
00:05:34.250 --> 00:05:35.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:05:35.880 --> 00:05:37.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was honestly surprised
when I found out she goes</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:37.800 --> 00:05:39.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to our school.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:39.590 --> 00:05:41.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You know, while I'm
actually really glad that</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:41.550 --> 00:05:42.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're showing interest
in a girl other</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:43.010 --> 00:05:44.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than Shoko Makinohara,</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:44.590 --> 00:05:47.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel like this one might
be out of your league.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:47.140 --> 00:05:49.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I never said I was asking
her out much less falling</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:49.640 --> 00:05:51.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in love with her.
- Then what's your deal?</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:51.560 --> 00:05:52.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sorry.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:53.060 --> 00:05:54.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was thinking about
how I've never seen her</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:54.850 --> 00:05:56.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with people while at school.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:57.110 --> 00:05:59.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's always by herself here.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:59.480 --> 00:06:02.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, good morning, Yuma.
- Morning, Kamisato.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:06:02.450 --> 00:06:04.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll catch up with you later,
Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:06:05.320 --> 00:06:06.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [scoffs]</b></Default>

c0000095
00:06:12.830 --> 00:06:15.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I heard this
from someone on my team.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:06:15.170 --> 00:06:17.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Apparently at the beginning
of her first year,</b></Default>

c0000097
00:06:17.670 --> 00:06:20.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakurajima didn't show up
to school even once.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:06:20.670 --> 00:06:22.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why not?
- 'Cause work.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:06:22.920 --> 00:06:25.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She mentioned going on hiatus
right when she got out</b></Default>

c0000100
00:06:25.390 --> 00:06:27.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of middle school but there
were jobs she was locked into</b></Default>

c0000101
00:06:27.640 --> 00:06:28.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>way before that.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:06:29.310 --> 00:06:31.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess those obligations
kept her busy.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:06:32.180 --> 00:06:34.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He said she didn't start coming
to school regularly</b></Default>

c0000104
00:06:34.190 --> 00:06:35.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until after summer break.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:06:36.020 --> 00:06:38.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's pretty rough timing.
- Right?</b></Default>

c0000106
00:06:39.820 --> 00:06:41.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mai Sakurajima.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:06:41.530 --> 00:06:43.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The celebrity that
started school midway through</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:43.450 --> 00:06:45.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the first year is an outsider.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:46.780 --> 00:06:48.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once a class forms its shape,</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:48.990 --> 00:06:50.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it doesn't change all
that easily.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:51.580 --> 00:06:54.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you stand out then others
will talk behind your back,</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:54.370 --> 00:06:57.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>saying you're annoying
or you're showing off.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:57.670 --> 00:07:00.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And everyone knows there's
no chance of turning back</b></Default>

c0000114
00:07:00.170 --> 00:07:02.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>once that happens.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:07:02.460 --> 00:07:04.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's just the kind
of place school is.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:07:05.550 --> 00:07:08.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No one is able to approach her
or talk to her.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:07:08.930 --> 00:07:11.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They don't want to be isolated
for standing out.</b></Default>

c0000118
00:07:12.390 --> 00:07:15.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why Sakurajima's taking
the hint and doing her best</b></Default>

c0000119
00:07:15.690 --> 00:07:17.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to try to blend
with the atmosphere.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:07:17.850 --> 00:07:19.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know it.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:07:19.690 --> 00:07:21.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, you and I need to talk.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:07:22.940 --> 00:07:24.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to get straight
to the point.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:07:24.690 --> 00:07:26.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Moving forward,
don't talk to Yuma.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:07:26.700 --> 00:07:28.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I really don't think
me talking to him</b></Default>

c0000125
00:07:28.660 --> 00:07:31.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is endangering your guys'
relationship, Kamisato.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:07:31.370 --> 00:07:32.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You know that's not
what I mean!</b></Default>

c0000127
00:07:33.450 --> 00:07:35.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is about
the hospitalization incident.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:07:36.370 --> 00:07:39.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, yeah.
I suppose everyone's heard, huh?</b></Default>

c0000129
00:07:39.250 --> 00:07:41.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If Yuma spends too much time
with a class loner like you,</b></Default>

c0000130
00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:43.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>his popularity's gonna plummet,</b></Default>

c0000131
00:07:43.800 --> 00:07:45.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I can't let that happen
to him.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:47.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, if we're going
by that logic,</b></Default>

c0000133
00:07:47.680 --> 00:07:50.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your own popularity is taking
a nosedive right now.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:50.430 --> 00:07:51.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You okay with that?</b></Default>

c0000135
00:07:51.890 --> 00:07:52.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you picking a fight?</b></Default>

c0000136
00:07:52.970 --> 00:07:54.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You picked one first.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:07:54.560 --> 00:07:56.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why so angry?
Is it that time of the month?</b></Default>

c0000138
00:07:56.730 --> 00:07:57.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000139
00:07:58.270 --> 00:08:00.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just die!
You're the worst!</b></Default>

c0000140
00:08:00.230 --> 00:08:01.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seriously, I hope you die!</b></Default>

c0000141
00:08:01.730 --> 00:08:03.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- At the end of the day,</b></Default>

c0000142
00:08:03.360 --> 00:08:06.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>everyone says cliche things
like, "I'm bored,"</b></Default>

c0000143
00:08:06.700 --> 00:08:09.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or, "Isn't there anything
interesting out there?"</b></Default>

c0000144
00:08:09.820 --> 00:08:12.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But not one of them
is seeking any real change.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:08:24.460 --> 00:08:25.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[machine beeps]</b></Default>

c0000146
00:08:29.550 --> 00:08:32.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, that's Mai Sakurajima,
isn't it?</b></Default>

c0000147
00:08:32.430 --> 00:08:34.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Where?
- Right there!</b></Default>

c0000148
00:08:34.930 --> 00:08:37.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's totally her!
I'll take a pic just in case.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:08:37.390 --> 00:08:38.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah?</b></Default>

c0000150
00:08:38.690 --> 00:08:39.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah, man.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:08:39.940 --> 00:08:41.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could she turn this way more?</b></Default>

c0000152
00:08:41.980 --> 00:08:43.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[stammers]
Huh?</b></Default>

c0000153
00:08:43.650 --> 00:08:45.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What--what the hell are you--</b></Default>

c0000154
00:08:46.190 --> 00:08:48.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm a human.
And what are you?</b></Default>

c0000155
00:08:48.110 --> 00:08:49.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A creepy photographer?</b></Default>

c0000156
00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:50.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
You little--</b></Default>

c0000157
00:08:50.950 --> 00:08:52.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think that's enough.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:08:52.280 --> 00:08:53.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should go now.
- [scoffs]</b></Default>

c0000159
00:08:54.120 --> 00:08:55.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's with that guy?</b></Default>

c0000160
00:08:55.620 --> 00:08:56.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's just a picture!</b></Default>

c0000161
00:09:02.290 --> 00:09:03.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thank you for that.</b></Default>

c0000162
