c0000232
00:11:54.300 --> 00:11:55.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What was all that yesterday?</b></Default>

c0000233
00:11:58.590 --> 00:12:02.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I was six when I made
