00:16:11.640 --> 00:16:14.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh!
- Don't make weird noises.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:16:14.220 --> 00:16:17.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's kinda sensitive there
so be gentle, please.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:16:17.810 --> 00:16:20.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How's this?
- It feels amazing.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:16:20.940 --> 00:16:23.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, ow, let go!
- How about this?</b></Default>

c0000328
00:16:23.270 --> 00:16:25.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Gentle enough for you?</b></Default>

c0000329
00:16:25.190 --> 00:16:27.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So what caused
a wound like that?</b></Default>

c0000330
00:16:28.360 --> 00:16:30.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, I don't actually know.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:16:34.870 --> 00:16:37.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is my sister Kaede.
- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000332
00:16:38.500 --> 00:16:40.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She wasn't assaulted
or anything.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:16:40.790 --> 00:16:42.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's from being bullied on
the internet.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:16:43.170 --> 00:16:45.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm not quite sure
what you're getting at.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:16:45.590 --> 00:16:48.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She didn't reply to a message
she got or something.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:16:48.970 --> 00:16:51.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So a popular girl in her class
started hating her,</b></Default>

c0000337
00:16:51.550 --> 00:16:53.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it led to people writing
horrible things about her</b></Default>

c0000338
00:16:53.800 --> 00:16:54.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on social media.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:16:56.680 --> 00:16:58.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then one day...</b></Default>

c0000340
00:16:58.480 --> 00:17:00.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, welcome home.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:17:00.980 --> 00:17:04.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big brother.
- Hmm? What's wrong?</b></Default>

c0000342
00:17:06.440 --> 00:17:07.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpers]</b></Default>

c0000343
00:17:08.400 --> 00:17:09.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000344
00:17:11.950 --> 00:17:14.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What happened to me
and my sister is why I believe</b></Default>

c0000345
00:17:14.450 --> 00:17:16.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>puberty syndrome
actually exists.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:17:17.250 --> 00:17:18.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yours occurred back then, too?</b></Default>

c0000347
00:17:20.540 --> 00:17:22.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I still don't know how or why.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:17:22.580 --> 00:17:24.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suddenly woke up covered
in blood,</b></Default>

c0000349
00:17:24.670 --> 00:17:25.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then was hospitalized.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:17:25.920 --> 00:17:27.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000351
00:17:27.260 --> 00:17:30.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, so
the hospitalization incident--</b></Default>

c0000352
00:17:30.090 --> 00:17:33.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah. It was me that
was sent to the hospital.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:17:34.050 --> 00:17:35.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big brother, are you in here?</b></Default>

c0000354
00:17:37.270 --> 00:17:38.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So--so sorry!</b></Default>

c0000355
00:17:38.980 --> 00:17:40.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Next time you rent a girlfriend,</b></Default>

c0000356
00:17:40.520 --> 00:17:42.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>please tell me in advance
so I know not to bother you!</b></Default>

c0000357
00:17:42.980 --> 00:17:44.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede, you really
shouldn't jump</b></Default>

c0000358
00:17:44.770 --> 00:17:46.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to conclusions like that.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:17:46.320 --> 00:17:48.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then is she making you buy
a vase?</b></Default>

c0000360
00:17:48.320 --> 00:17:49.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Not even close.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:17:49.400 --> 00:17:51.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She's selling English lessons?</b></Default>

c0000362
00:17:51.320 --> 00:17:53.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I promise she's not here
to sell anything.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:17:53.570 --> 00:17:55.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She is an upper classman
from my school.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:17:56.490 --> 00:17:59.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm Mai Sakurajima.
Nice to meet you.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:17:59.160 --> 00:18:00.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000366
00:18:00.450 --> 00:18:01.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000367
00:18:02.120 --> 00:18:04.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My name's Kaeda Azusagawa.
Pleasure.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:18:05.540 --> 00:18:06.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Let's see.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:18:06.790 --> 00:18:08.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said, "My name's
Kaede Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:11.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A pleasure."
[cat meows]</b></Default>

c0000371
00:18:11.630 --> 00:18:13.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And this is Nasuno.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:18:13.510 --> 00:18:16.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"And this is Nasuno,"
is what that one was.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:18:16.970 --> 00:18:19.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I appreciate you letting
me know, Kaede. Thank you.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:18:19.810 --> 00:18:21.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000375
00:18:21.810 --> 00:18:23.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpers]
- Sorry about that.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:18:23.980 --> 00:18:25.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's terrified of strangers.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:18:25.980 --> 00:18:27.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These days she loves
the house so much,</b></Default>

c0000378
00:18:27.860 --> 00:18:29.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she doesn't go
to school anymore.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:18:29.480 --> 00:18:31.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It seemed like she
didn't recognize me.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:18:31.820 --> 00:18:32.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, yeah.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:18:33.740 --> 00:18:35.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's not that into TV.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:18:36.530 --> 00:18:39.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For her, distancing herself
from the internet helped</b></Default>

c0000383
00:18:40.040 --> 00:18:42.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with lessening the symptoms
of puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:18:42.750 --> 00:18:44.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's actually the reason
I threw my smartphone</b></Default>

c0000385
00:18:44.710 --> 00:18:45.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into the sea.</b></Default>

c0000386
00:18:45.790 --> 00:18:47.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So are you trying to tell me</b></Default>

c0000387
00:18:47.630 --> 00:18:49.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that my case is similar
to all this?</b></Default>

c0000388
00:18:49.420 --> 00:18:50.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're too good at your job.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:18:51.050 --> 00:18:54.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At school you play the role
of the atmosphere perfectly.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:18:54.590 --> 00:18:58.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why in order to not make
the situation any worse for you,</b></Default>

c0000391
00:18:58.300 --> 00:19:00.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think it's probably better
for you to return</b></Default>

c0000392
00:19:00.350 --> 00:19:03.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to show business.
- Are you serious?</b></Default>

c0000393
00:19:03.520 --> 00:19:05.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You might still be playing
the atmosphere</b></Default>

c0000394
00:19:05.390 --> 00:19:07.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but if you keep standing out
on TV,</b></Default>

c0000395
00:19:07.440 --> 00:19:09.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>people won't be able
to ignore you.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:19:10.230 --> 00:19:13.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Plus I kinda get the feeling
you're dying to go back, anyway.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:19:13.820 --> 00:19:16.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm curious to what
gave you that idea.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:19:16.490 --> 00:19:18.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- When we were on the train,</b></Default>

c0000399
00:19:18.370 --> 00:19:20.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I saw you giving an envious look
while staring up</b></Default>

c0000400
00:19:20.580 --> 00:19:21.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at that movie ad.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:19:22.950 --> 00:19:25.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think you should do what
your heart tells you to.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:19:26.040 --> 00:19:28.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have the talent
and experience.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:19:28.460 --> 00:19:30.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even your manager
is eagerly awaiting your return.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:19:30.340 --> 00:19:31.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- This doesn't concern her.</b></Default>

c0000405
00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:34.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really need
to mind your own business.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:19:35.340 --> 00:19:36.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [stammers]</b></Default>

c0000407
00:19:36.800 --> 00:19:39.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, the bathroom is--
- I'm going home now.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:19:40.100 --> 00:19:42.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Wait, what about--
- You can have it.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:19:45.730 --> 00:19:46.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000410
00:19:48.600 --> 00:19:52.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since then, Mai hasn't been
showing up to school.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:19:53.530 --> 00:19:57.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It appears that I stepped on
 a monumental mine of some sort.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:19:58.160 --> 00:20:00.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I dug a little deeper
than I should have.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:20:06.080 --> 00:20:07.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000414
00:20:12.290 --> 00:20:14.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Kunimi.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:20:14.170 --> 00:20:16.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you know why Mai Sakurajima
went on hiatus</b></Default>

c0000416
00:20:16.720 --> 00:20:18.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the entertainment industry?</b></Default>

c0000417
00:20:18.300 --> 00:20:20.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I heard it was so she
could concentrate on studying</b></Default>

c0000418
00:20:20.760 --> 00:20:22.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but that's all she told
the public.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:20:22.810 --> 00:20:25.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa, it looks like that
reporter lady's here again.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:20:28.730 --> 00:20:30.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, hey.
It's been a while.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:20:30.190 --> 00:20:32.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sorry, but have we met before?</b></Default>

c0000422
00:20:32.400 --> 00:20:34.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So that's how
you're gonna play, huh?</b></Default>

c0000423
00:20:34.570 --> 00:20:36.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, then,
it's nice to meet you.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:20:36.940 --> 00:20:38.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My info's on my business card.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:20:40.490 --> 00:20:42.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What can I do for you today,
ma'am?</b></Default>

c0000426
00:20:42.620 --> 00:20:45.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I was covering
a story about young sardines.</b></Default>

c0000427
00:20:45.370 --> 00:20:48.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And since I was in the area,
I thought I'd drop by.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:20:48.330 --> 00:20:49.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's your order?</b></Default>

c0000429
00:20:49.750 --> 00:20:52.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'd like one Sakuta to go,
please.</b></Default>

c0000430
00:20:52.170 --> 00:20:55.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sorry to inform you but we're
not that kind of establishment.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:20:55.340 --> 00:20:57.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You may wanna try
looking elsewhere.</b></Default>

c0000432
00:20:57.380 --> 00:21:00.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You still won't talk even
a little bit about the incident?</b></Default>

c0000433
00:21:00.760 --> 00:21:02.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll never talk about it.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:21:02.390 --> 00:21:04.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then how about you let
me take a picture</b></Default>

c0000435
00:21:04.260 --> 00:21:06.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the scar on your chest
and we'll call it a day?</b></Default>

c0000436
00:21:06.310 --> 00:21:07.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, thank you.</b></Default>

c0000437
00:21:09.100 --> 00:21:11.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unrelated subject,
but do you happen to know</b></Default>

c0000438
00:21:11.310 --> 00:21:13.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the reason Mai Sakurajima
went on hiatus?</b></Default>

c0000439
00:21:13.650 --> 00:21:14.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000440
00:21:15.900 --> 00:21:18.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I know a few things that
the average person might not.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:21:18.610 --> 00:21:20.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've done some researching.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:21:22.410 --> 00:21:24.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000443
00:21:27.500 --> 00:21:29.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So, I've been hearing that
you're head-over-heels</b></Default>

c0000444
00:21:29.410 --> 00:21:31.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for Sakurajima these days.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:21:31.210 --> 00:21:34.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does that mean you've gotten
over Shoko Makinohara?</b></Default>

c0000446
00:21:34.210 --> 00:21:37.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How did you and Kunimi
both jump to that conclusion?</b></Default>

c0000447
00:21:37.340 --> 00:21:39.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Here's some sugar
if you want it.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:21:39.630 --> 00:21:41.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You sure this is safe
to consume?</b></Default>

c0000449
00:21:42.220 --> 00:21:43.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I mean, it's probably sugar.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:21:43.640 --> 00:21:44.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is white.</b></Default>

c0000451
00:21:45.220 --> 00:21:47.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, then,
what did you wanna ask me?</b></Default>

c0000452
00:21:47.850 --> 00:21:50.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, do you think
it's possible</b></Default>

c0000453
00:21:50.270 --> 00:21:51.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to lose sight of someone?</b></Default>

c0000454
00:21:51.940 --> 00:21:54.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- See an optometrist
if you're having eye problems.</b></Default>

c0000455
00:21:54.520 --> 00:21:56.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's not the issue, Futaba.</b></Default>

c0000456
00:21:56.650 --> 00:21:59.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like, what if someone is there
but you can't see them because</b></Default>

c0000457
00:21:59.780 --> 00:22:01.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they've become invisible?</b></Default>

c0000458
00:22:01.280 --> 00:22:03.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you trying to think
of how to sneak into</b></Default>

c0000459
00:22:03.160 --> 00:22:05.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the girls' bathroom?
Oh, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0000460
00:22:05.700 --> 00:22:08.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are such a rascal.
- Don't accuse me of that.</b></Default>

c0000461
00:22:09.040 --> 00:22:11.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you came here
to talk about puberty syndrome,</b></Default>

c0000462
00:22:11.290 --> 00:22:13.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I may have already told
you this but I don't actually</b></Default>

c0000463
00:22:13.790 --> 00:22:15.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>believe it's a real thing.</b></Default>

c0000464
00:22:15.080 --> 00:22:17.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I know.
You said it's not logical.</b></Default>

c0000465
00:22:17.960 --> 00:22:20.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I came here 'cause I thought
you could help me understand.</b></Default>

c0000466
00:22:21.300 --> 00:22:24.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So if I'm sitting right in front
of you exactly like I am now,</b></Default>

c0000467
00:22:24.720 --> 00:22:26.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>could I just become invisible
to you?</b></Default>

c0000468
00:22:26.720 --> 00:22:28.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that even possible?</b></Default>

c0000469
00:22:28.260 --> 00:22:30.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- All I need to do
is get engrossed in something</b></Default>

c0000470
00:22:30.520 --> 00:22:31.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or simply space out.</b></Default>

c0000471
00:22:32.520 --> 00:22:34.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Human brains don't
really notice things</b></Default>

c0000472
00:22:34.440 --> 00:22:35.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that they don't want to see.</b></Default>

c0000473
00:22:35.690 --> 00:22:38.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- True, but what
if that's not quite it?</b></Default>

c0000474
00:22:38.360 --> 00:22:40.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then there's also
the measurement theory.</b></Default>

c0000475
00:22:40.480 --> 00:22:42.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What does that entail?</b></Default>

c0000476
00:22:42.440 --> 00:22:44.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's the theory that
the existence</b></Default>

c0000477
00:22:44.200 --> 00:22:46.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of something in this world
is only confirmed to be real</b></Default>

c0000478
00:22:46.870 --> 00:22:48.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the moment someone
observes it.</b></Default>

c0000479
00:22:49.330 --> 00:22:50.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Surely you know
the famous example</b></Default>

c0000480
00:22:51.040 --> 00:22:52.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of it involving the cat in
the box.</b></Default>

c0000481
00:22:53.040 --> 00:22:55.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Right, what was that, again?</b></Default>

c0000482
00:22:56.040 --> 00:22:58.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's called
Schrodinger's Cat.</b></Default>

c0000483
00:23:02.170 --> 00:23:05.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- With Mai Sakurajima being
a star in the public eye,</b></Default>

c0000484
00:23:05.470 --> 00:23:07.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it meant everyone
was observing her.</b></Default>

c0000485
00:23:09.810 --> 00:23:11.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One custard-filled bun, please.</b></Default>

c0000486
00:23:11.680 --> 00:23:13.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- All right,
let me grab that for you.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:23:15.100 --> 00:23:18.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Do you happen to know
who Mai Sakurajima is?</b></Default>

c0000488
00:23:18.480 --> 00:23:20.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mm?
- Ah, you know.</b></Default>

c0000489
00:23:20.480 --> 00:23:22.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The child actress who made
her debut by getting cast</b></Default>

c0000490
00:23:22.820 --> 00:23:24.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in a popular morning drama.</b></Default>

c0000491
00:23:24.360 --> 00:23:26.110 line:90% align:center
