00:23:40.630 --> 00:23:41.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000497
00:23:42.380 --> 00:23:44.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0000498
00:23:56.480 --> 00:23:58.020 line:90% align:center
